Package camp

Class RegisteredCampsPrinter

  • Object
    • RegisteredCampsPrinter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPrintRegisteredCamps
    public class RegisteredCampsPrinter
extends Object
implements IPrintRegisteredCamps
    Represents an class that takes in a list that holds the names of the registered camps, as well as the corresponding role of the student. It then looks through the camp database and prints all details of those camps, as well as the role the student has in the camp.
    Since:
    2023-11-17
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Soo Qi Yang, Teo Kai Xuan, Masagca Merwyn Louie Dumasis, Nguyen Phuong Linh, Tee Jeeng Yee
